    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8243357>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. A–H. Rohdea chloroxantha. A. Habitat. B. Aerial parts discarded after harvesting rhizomes. C. Stolons. D. Lateral bud. E, F & G. Cultivated plants. H. Blade. I. Stolon of R. grandiflora. J. Stolon of R. pachynema." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8243357/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8243359>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Rohdea chloroxantha. A. Habit. B. Inflorescence. C. Mature flower. D. Freshly opened flower. E. Outer bract (left) and inner bract (right). F. Flower with perianth lobe removed. G. Flower in longitudinal section. H. Perianth tube in transverse section, bottom view. I. Flower with perianth lobe and stamens removed. J. Flower in vertical view and show the base of filaments. K. Flower in lateral view. L. Partial perianths with stamen removed from near base, ventral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8243359/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8243361>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. A. Rohdea pachynema. A1, inflorescence;A2, mature flower;A3, flower in longitudinal section.A4, flower with perianth lobe removed; A5, partial perianths with stamens, ventral view; A6, one partial perianth with stamen, ventral view. B. R. fargesii var. fargesii. B1, inflorescence; B2, mature flower; B3, Flower with stamens removed; B4, flower in longitudinal section; B5, two partial perianths with stamens, ventral view; B6, some partial perianths with stamen, ventral view. C. R. chloroxantha. C1, inflorescence; C2, mature flower; C3, flower in longitudinal section; C4, Flower with perianth lobe removed; C5, Flower with perianth lobe and stamens removed; C6, partial perianths with stamen removed from near base, ventral view. D. R. grandiflora. D1, inflorescence; D2, mature flower; D3, flower in longitudinal section; D4, two partial perianths with stamens, ventral view.A1–A6: These flowers are dipped in FAA soution." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8243361/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

